title: Nisekoi 2 - EP 11 (1080p)
description: Raku and the girls are back! The hunt for the key to his heart and locket continues in the second season of this fan favorite anime series. Nisekoi: features all the familiar characters from the first season joined by Kosaki's younger sister Haru. With a new girl entering the equation, will it really be "more the merrier" for Raku? What will happen to this false love?
